PALMER (William M.) on H.C S252145 Supreme Court of California. JANUARY 16, 2019

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. The Reporter of Decisions is directed not to publish in the Official Appellate Reports the opinion in the above-entitled proceeding filed September 13, 2018 which appears at 27 Cal.App.5th 120, 238 Cal.Rptr.3d 59. ( Cal. Const., art. VI, section 14 ; Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.1125(c)(1).)
